content.html: You’re not voting Labour or LibDem to get the party of your dreams. You’re voting Labour or LibDem to defeat the Tories and change our voting system. THEN you can vote for the party of your dreams. Meantime: suck it up.
content.value:
You’re not voting Labour or LibDem to get the party of your dreams. You’re voting Labour or LibDem to defeat the Tories and change our voting system. 

THEN you can vote for the party of your dreams. 

Meantime: suck it up.
